OL,2,MThe Hassle Hurdle: a philosophy to
OL,4,Mhack ADHD
OL,6,CAutumn Tulloch
OL,7,CFri 13:10-13:40
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GEight years ago a 5 second bit in a
OL,11,GYouTube video led me to develop a
OL,12,Ggeneralised philosophy on how to
OL,13,Gdesign coping mechanisms for my ADHD:
OL,14,GThe Hassle Hurdle. Ever since then
OL,15,GI've been continuously using and
OL,16,Gimproving the philosophy to manage the
OL,17,Gsymptoms of my ADHD, and my quality of
OL,18,Glife in general. In the talk I'll
OL,19,Gintroduce the three rules of the
OL,20,Gphilosophy, how they came about, and
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
